735
00:35:22,590 --> 00:35:23,760
His name is...

736
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:24,960
His name is Sun Xiaoguang,

737
00:35:25,190 --> 00:35:26,590
abducted at two years old

738
00:35:27,110 --> 00:35:29,750
around Jinxiuyuan
at Fushan West Gardens.

739
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:38,320
Drink some water.

